FT  01 JAN 94 / World News in Brief: Smoke-free to Australia and New Zealand
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
British Airways is to ban smoking for a trial period on flights between the
UK and Australia and New Zealand. The airline's domestic and short-haul
European flights are already non-smoking.
